title: Kairat Boranbayev
text: Kairat Sovetaiuly Boranbayev (, "Qaırat Sovetaıuly Boranbaev"; born September 22, 1966) is a <a href="Kazakhstan">Kazakh</a> businessman and <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Administrator%20%28business%29">administrator</a> who has served as the <a href="FC%20Kairat">Football Club Kairat</a> president of the <a href="Kazakhstan%20Premier%20League">Kazakhstan Premier League</a>.
